description:
Dream Wisely is currently available for an ongoing Hotel Lounge, Rooftop Bar or Beach Resort DJ Residency in Asia & Worldwide. Also for one-off local or International events.

A Chilled Deep Jazz House / Hotel Lounge Bar style DJ mix put together for a DJ residency application where the client requested more Jazz in the mix. This was the type of thing I used to perform at my previous DJ residency at the Lebua Hotel.

Tracks From: Tim Deluxe, DJ Hell, Adam Byrd, Inkfish, MoodyManc, J&M Brothers, Prosis, D-Nox & Beckers, Olderic, Oniris, Sumo, Shur-I-Kan, Soulmelt, Nick Curly, Uner

description:
It's with great pleasure we release mix number 2 for 2013, and Christopher Tubbs' tenth in the series.

If you haven't been in person to the Heads Down Sessions at Caravan, it's 6 hours of Balearica, disco, leftfield soul and a plethora of the weird and wonderful played to a gastrosonic crowd fuelled by some of the best tapas style cuisine and cocktails in London.

The next Caravan session is tomorrow, Saturday June the 17th at 6pm.

http://www.headsdown.org

description:
Gerd Janson and I played back to back at the Circoloco x Loveland party a couple of weeks ago at ADE. We had a lot of fun and the recording came out pretty nice! So we decided to share it with you guys...

Gerd's wicked new Fabric CD is out now. Check it: http://www.fabriclondon.com/store/fabric-89.html

Jackmaster facebook page is here: http://facebook.com/djjackmaster

Photo by Sebastian Manox for Warehouse Project!

Upcoming shows from the two of us:
